	(text "Design Notes\n\n• Encoder A, B, SW configured\n  as INPUT_PULLUP in firmware.\n\n• Encoder Common connected\n  to GND.\n\n• PWM output: Arduino D9.\n\n• IRLZ44N gate protected by\n  220Ω series resistor and\n  10kΩ pull-down resistor.\n\n• Flyback diode required\n  across motor terminals."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
